{"article_id":"MVcVgpnbEwsqgKxd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Until average Americans feel the cuts ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"neither side looks willing to budge .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The age of austerity ?","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"President Barack Obama and congressional Republicans are dug in on the sequester ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"and there are no signs of a quick fix to the $ 85 billion in across-the-board spending cuts","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that both sides say","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"they disdain .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"That could certainly change after a few bad months of economic numbers or a public outcry .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"until average Americans feel the cuts ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"neither side looks willing to budge on the key issue of revenues","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"without some game-changing factor .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"And neither party is inclined to risk a government shutdown on sequester politics .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"anyone quite understands","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"how the sequester is really going to work , \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"( R-Ohio )","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"conceded in an interview","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"aired Sunday on NBC ' s \" Meet the Press . \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Below are ' S three possible scenarios for how the next several weeks play out .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The cuts were designed in 2011","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to be so onerous","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that nobody would want to keep them in place .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"But 18 months and several unfulfilling budget battles later , Republicans came to accept sequestration as the only guaranteed way","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to slice the government ' s bottom line .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"And maybe , just maybe , it won ' t be as bad","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"as Obama , Democrats , independent economists and even many Republicans expect .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Boehner penned a Wall Street Journal op-ed last month","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"claiming","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"the sequester \" threatens U.S. national security , thousands of jobs and more , \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"but he backtracked a bit on \" Meet the Press , \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" I don ' t know","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"whether it ' s going to hurt the economy or not . \"","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Congress could take up measures","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to ease the impact ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"possibly with legislation","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"giving department heads the ability","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to better target the cuts .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"A Republican-sponsored bill","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"aimed at this goal","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"failed in the Senate last week ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"but a Senate Democratic leadership aide said","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"it could be rewritten","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"to attract Democrats , particularly those from military states ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"who would be anxious to show constituents","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that they ' re doing something","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"- even if it puts them at odds with the president .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"House Republicans are planning to also vote on a bill with language","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"to help make the budget cuts more manageable for the military and veterans .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"But administration officials argue","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that even the added flexibility wouldn ' t change the bottom line .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"\" There is no way","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that you can move the deck chairs around in a way","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"that will not cost our economy ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"as [ the Congressional Budget Office ]","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"projects , 750,000 jobs , \"","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"White House economics adviser Gene Sperling said Sunday on ABC ' s \" This Week. \"","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"\" When you have those types of harsh spending cuts in such a short , concentrated period of time ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"it is like saying to somebody ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"' You can cut off three of your fingers ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"but you can have the flexibility","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"to choose which ones you want to cut off . ' \"","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"If the sequester stays in place through the end of the fiscal year in September ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"it would mark a new era in Washington :","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"a temporary stall in emergency budget wars ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"which have dominated Washington","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"since Republicans took over the House in 2011 .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"The debt limit won ' t need to be raised until May at the earliest","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"- that could even stretch until August ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"according to calculations by some top-level aides .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"And the prevailing wisdom in the Capitol is that House Republicans can not demand anything in exchange for extending the country ' s borrowing authority .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Democrats argue","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that the GOP lost the right do that","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"when it agreed to lift the ceiling in January","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"without insisting on an equal amount of cuts .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":78,"right":152,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":